parts:
I like confirming facts by calculated (but certainly not overdrawn) acts of restraint;

Aurora, I would hold _us_ there long enough for those ever so slightest barely perceptible squirms of aching to match and resonate by that characteristic I know we know.

And then I would be a bit bold, and afford you the simple choice to slide onto me, the proper bodyhole pairing completion; then honestly, have your way on top of me dear, you deserve it. Your weight, your corresponding colors' dynamics, your harmonic motion commanding my damping, please as much as your energetics desire.
